 planet from ecological collapse for years to come.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 20. Sep 2019) 0aEnvironmental ethics. 0aReligion and science. 70(DE-601)1041808540(DE-588)4078520-8aUmweltethik2gnd 70(DE-601)1042888330(DE-588)4041358-5aNatur2gnd 70(DE-601)1061871550(DE-588)4049396-9aReligion2gnd 70(DE-601)1062193240(DE-588)4041421-8aNaturwissenschaften2gnd 70(DE-601)2374990100(DE-588)4479722-9aSakralisierung2gnd 7aRELIGION / Religion & Science.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUC Press eBook-Package 2016-2018z978311063539308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUC Press eBook-Package 2017z978311066755408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUCal Press eBook Package Frontlist 2017-2018z978311065859040uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/9780520967908423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780520967908.jpg  a978-3-11-063539-3  UC Press eBook-Package 2016-2018c2016d2018  a978-3-11-065859-0  UCal Press eBook Package Frontlist 2017-2018c2017d2018  a978-3-11-066755-4  UC Press eBook-Package 2017b2017  aGBV-deGruyter-alles